{"tid":453404,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有bipolar disorder 鬱燥症?","createTime":"2017-10-31T07:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T08:11:52.000Z","uid":134364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f99492da120db8ec744a05920dd6bfe018d3c123","tid":453404,"uid":134364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:07:00.000Z","msg":"可唔可以分享下manic 同 depressive state 嗰陣係點? Manic 同 happiness 又有咩分別?"},{"pid":"013d53240b4ce9994670fdb14d709488b02a008c","tid":453404,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T07:31:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%BA%81%E9%AC%B1%E7%97%87?wprov=sfsi1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25BA%2581%25E9%25AC%25B1%25E7%2597%2587%3Fwprov%3Dsfsi1&d=buFYMUadxM7cOVM0KOViTF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=5d9ce77f\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%BA%81%E9%AC%B1%E7%97%87?wprov=sfsi1</a><br />\n雖然係維基"},{"pid":"f29de88e5eb8c08aae1f56d6a602bc08b0ee29bf","tid":453404,"uid":47722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"我條女就喺呢個病嘅病患者，不過我識佢嘅時候已經開始有食藥。<br />\n以我理解，呢個病基本上有2個 情況<br />\n<br />\n第1個情況 會令佢好集中且不停咁做某樣野，所以會搞到好夜都瞓唔到。情緒會keep 住高漲，做事沉迷到不顧後果（eg.不顧休息）。<br />\n<br />\n第2個情況就 類似抑鬱，會好怕見人同店到人，會對好多野都無安全感，唔想出街，會唔鐘意自己呢一個存在。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲都喺我從我女朋友到聽翻黎嘅，佢仲話呢2個情況會keep住交替。<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢已經有食藥，但我同佢一齊嘅時候都會feel到佢好無安全感，好容易驚同唔開心，會好依賴我，經常發惡夢，所以我嘅做法就喺經常喺佢身邊陪佢，喺佢唔開心嘅時候讚佢同開解佢。<br />\n<br />\n最後要重點同你講嘅就喺，呢個病 食藥好重要，晚晚都要食藥，如果唔食嘅話第二日就會頭痛作嘔作悶。<br />\n<br />\n至於藥物方面，食完啲藥會令人好眼瞓，好易起唔到身。<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabae626a1ee56e9810d8a28538a3845cf8ca932","tid":453404,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T08:11:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以分享下manic 同 depressive state 嗰陣係點? Manic 同 happiness 又有咩分別?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMania<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mania\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FMania&d=buFYMUadxM7cOVM0KOViTF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=1b8dc5eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mania</a><br />\n<br />\n自己搵 google 啦"}]}